  "description": [
    "BIG STOCK DIVIDEND FULLY DISCOUNTED Standard Oil of N J Drops Twenty PointsGeneral j Market Is Firm BY STUART P WKST By Special Leased Wire to The Star NEW YORK October 13 Announcement of the recapitalization plan of the Standard OiJ of New Jersey with its 400 per cent stock dividend was the first consideration before the stock market today The discovery that the splitup of the share capital would mean nothing extra at least immediately for j shareholders seemed to occasion genuine disappointment The street promptly drew the inference that the 50 points advance in the stock within the previous two weeks had greatly overdone things and there was a rush tn coii which caused a tenDoint break right at the opening and a total drop of more than twenty points later on Inasmuch as the incentive for a good deal of the recent speculation has laid in the supposed stimulus of this and similar plans for capital readjustment the collapse in Standard Oil shares furnished a pretty severe test for the market as a whole It did hit the oil shares rather hard putting a stop to further attempts at speculation for the rise in tins Quarter Hut"
  ],
